Just a quick map i whipped up there will more than likely be updates to it
i used karatekafer's zombie skybox texture
you're all fighting on top of platforms in the water if you fall in the water you will either die or get lucky and get to live with 50 hp all the places to jump to are lit up with lights 

you should also enable the flashlight for this map it does help
